</div></div><div class="col-xs-12 indexcon indexcon33 szy2"><div data-aos="flip-left"  class="col-xs-12  col-md-4 kin1"><div class="abeiprn"></div><div class="col-xs-12 reservepadding"><div class="gki1"><a href="aboutus.html"><span>ABOUT</span> 關於森典</a></div>

<div class="aboutne">
<p class="peinr" style="text-align: justify;">森典希望在這個忙碌的城市裡，能給寶貝探索事物和盡情發揮自己的小天地。</p>

<p class="peinr" style="text-align: justify;">我們深信用愛及鼓勵的教育環境來陪伴寶貝長大，就像小小幼苗，給予它足夠養份，它會朝著有陽光的方向長大，幸福是環境及心靈的富足~</p>

<p class="peinr" style="text-align: justify;">森典打造童趣的故事書景象，並結合貓頭鷹的初心象徵守護、智慧，我們秉持森典就像森林裡的字典，大自然的典範來鼓勵、祝福寶貝。</p>

<p class="peinr" style="text-align: justify;">我們以多元學習、激發創造力，建立人文與愛的氛圍，讓寶貝訓練獨立性，從小幼苗慢慢長大，最後蛻變成小樹，經得起挑戰，開始勇敢表達，直到成為我們都引以為傲的大樹！</p>

<div class="col-xs-12"><a class="jiprper" href="aboutus.html"><img src="/uploads/sendian/images/202205310742374390.png" /></a></div>
</div>
</div></div><div data-aos="flip-left"  class="col-xs-12  col-md-4 kin2"><div class="abeiprn"></div><div class="col-xs-12  titlekin2"><a href="contents-1.html">園內消息<br /><span>NEWS</span></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 reservepadding"><div class="col-xs-12 indexnews2"><a href="content-37.html"><span class="col-xs-3 col-md-3 newsimgs" ><img src="/uploads/news/202602/480_480/20260220222824e156.jpg" /></span ><span  class="col-xs-9 col-md-9"><span class="indexnewsb">2026-02-15</span ><span class="indexnewst2">Happy New Year</span></span></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 indexnews2"><a href="content-36.html"><span class="col-xs-3 col-md-3 newsimgs" ><img src="/uploads/news/202512/480_480/202512201739527726.jpg" /></span ><span  class="col-xs-9 col-md-9"><span class="indexnewsb">2025-12-20</span ><span class="indexnewst2">115學年度、116學年度招生資訊</span></span></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 indexnews2"><a href="content-35.html"><span class="col-xs-3 col-md-3 newsimgs" ><img src="/uploads/news/202512/480_480/20251220173351d648.jpg" /></span ><span  class="col-xs-9 col-md-9"><span class="indexnewsb">2025-12-20</span ><span class="indexnewst2">Italy Culture Day</span></span></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12 indexnewmore"><a class="hipers jiprper" href="contents-1.html"></a></div></div></div><div data-aos="flip-left"  class="col-xs-12  col-md-4 kin3"><div class="abeiprn"></div><div class="col-xs-12 reservepadding"><div class="gfki1"><a href="philosophy.html">教學理念<br />
<span>philosophy</span></a></div>

<div class="ptopnrg">
